WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.080
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:02.080 --> 00:00:03.560
How are you all doing today?

00:00:03.560 --> 00:00:08.880
I’m going to talk to you about the angelic visitations I’ve had.

00:00:08.880 --> 00:00:19.560
I’ve had several angelic visitations over the years and the Lord has been amazing; I’ve seen some really cool stuff.

00:00:20.333 --> 00:00:23.309
This time, we were just praying.

00:00:23.309 --> 00:00:27.580
It was a normal night in the same house and everything was the same.

00:00:30.746 --> 00:00:36.163
We were praying and went to bed, and all of a sudden my wife and I were woken up out of our sleep.

00:00:39.360 --> 00:00:45.142
It was early in the morning and the whole house shook.

00:00:45.142 --> 00:00:53.741
It sounded like the whole roof was going to come off our house and my wife said, 'Oh, did you hear that?

00:00:53.741 --> 00:00:55.792
' She woke me and I said, 'Yes, I heard it.

00:00:55.792 --> 00:00:56.960
It woke me up, too.

00:00:57.280 --> 00:01:02.399
I think somebody’s trying to break into our house,' and I said, 'Let me go check.

00:01:02.399 --> 00:01:07.300
' I grabbed my pistol and went to check our home to make sure that nobody was there.

00:01:12.240 --> 00:01:16.622
All of a sudden, I looked out while standing by the door.

00:01:17.475 --> 00:01:23.947
I stood up and my eyes were opened to the spirit realm.

00:01:24.484 --> 00:01:29.500
I saw four demons.

00:01:36.954 --> 00:01:43.279
They were four demonic spirits covered with scales, with nasty-looking hair growing out of them and warts.

00:01:44.719 --> 00:01:49.079
Their eyes were slanted and red.

00:01:49.849 --> 00:01:53.860
One had a pig-looking nose with tusks coming up.

00:01:54.200 --> 00:02:00.266
The other was completely black; there was no shape to it.

00:02:00.266 --> 00:02:08.091
It looked kind of like a ghost, but it was just a black, misty-looking thing.

00:02:08.468 --> 00:02:10.109
The others were different shapes.

00:02:10.109 --> 00:02:17.020
I’m not going to give any more glory to it, but every single one of them was there, trying to get into the house.

00:02:19.618 --> 00:02:29.505
They shook the roof of the house in the natural, and like I said, it startled both of us and woke us up, but they couldn't get in.

00:02:29.505 --> 00:02:40.427
The Lord didn't show me this at the time, but I saw them grunting and hissing, carrying on while passing by on the street.

00:02:40.738 --> 00:02:43.200
I didn't understand why they couldn't come past.

00:02:43.660 --> 00:02:52.920
All of a sudden, I saw massive, humongous angels chained together.

00:02:52.920 --> 00:03:00.560
Their arms were linked together, like when you cross your arms with someone else; that’s how they were standing.

00:03:16.733 --> 00:03:17.280
They were standing strong, and the demonic spirits were hitting against those angelic beings, but they couldn't get past them.

00:03:37.646 --> 00:03:43.976
Every night before we go to bed, we put chain-linked angels all around our house and commission them.

00:03:43.976 --> 00:03:54.171
We thank you, Lord, that the angels are surrounding our house, that no devil in hell can come across the bloodline or the angels.

00:03:54.171 --> 00:04:01.360
The angels are protecting us as we sleep, just like we prayed.

00:04:05.689 --> 00:04:15.200
It took me aback so much that I yelled when I saw this, 'Praise God!

00:04:15.200 --> 00:04:16.106
Wow!

00:04:16.106 --> 00:04:18.466
Praise the Lord!

00:04:18.466 --> 00:04:36.263
' I saw the angels protecting us, and whenever they heard me praising the Lord, they all looked over, turned their bodies, and started looking at me, saying, 'Praise the Lord!

00:04:36.263 --> 00:04:39.760
' They started worshiping the Lord with me.

00:04:40.160 --> 00:04:42.240
I turned around and said, 'Whoa!

00:04:42.240 --> 00:04:45.659
' because it took me aback because it was so loud.

00:04:45.659 --> 00:04:53.760
Their voices were so loud it sounded like sirens, like trumpets, like a blast.

00:04:53.760 --> 00:04:55.049
'Praise the Lord!

00:04:55.049 --> 00:05:02.906
' They didn't say it individually; they said it together.

00:05:02.906 --> 00:05:08.920
They said, 'Praise the Lord,' and when they did, it echoed throughout the area.

00:05:08.920 --> 00:05:13.380
You could hear it in the spirit realm; it was so loud you would have to hold your ears.

00:05:15.853 --> 00:05:18.240
They started praising the Lord with me.

00:05:18.560 --> 00:05:29.226
Every time they worshiped, they turned to see what I was doing and as I praised the Lord, they started praising the Lord too.

00:05:32.960 --> 00:05:35.699
It became a chain and we just started praising the Lord.

00:05:35.699 --> 00:05:55.360
At that time, I saw the glory coming from the heavens through a portal, and I could see shafts of light coming through that portal, making those angels glow.

00:05:56.586 --> 00:06:03.806
They started glowing with a heavenly glory even brighter as they praised the Lord.

00:06:03.806 --> 00:06:16.360
Those shafts of light were coming out of the heavens and making them stronger—it was like it was giving them 'super juice.

00:06:16.360 --> 00:06:19.337
' They were praising the Lord with me and getting shinier.

00:06:24.160 --> 00:06:33.360
I had completely forgotten about the demonic spirits because I was caught up in the glory of worshiping the angels at the same time.

00:06:33.680 --> 00:06:38.013
Every time I said, 'Thank you, Jesus,' they would say, 'Thank you, Jesus.

00:06:38.013 --> 00:06:40.800
' This went on for quite some time.

00:06:46.212 --> 00:06:52.971
I was taken aback by what I was seeing in the spirit realm; it really was amazing.

00:06:52.971 --> 00:06:56.112
After all this happened, I saw the glory come down.

00:06:57.264 --> 00:07:02.399
It was around 4 or 5 in the morning now, and I had to go to work the next day by eight.

00:07:03.395 --> 00:07:07.360
I went and laid down a little bit and dozed off, but it was hard to get more rest.

00:07:10.720 --> 00:07:21.919
I got to work the next day at the church for an all-staff meeting and the pastor, Pastor Mark, saw me sitting in the front.

00:07:22.103 --> 00:07:25.131
I told him, 'I want to tell you what happened last night.

00:07:25.131 --> 00:07:27.760
' He said, 'Brandon, I don't doubt it at all.

00:07:28.400 --> 00:07:30.960
As you were talking, you were shining.

00:07:31.199 --> 00:07:33.577
I can see the glory shining on you.

00:07:33.577 --> 00:07:43.897
' There was actually a presence of the Lord on me from the visitation the night before, making me shine a little bit.

00:07:49.179 --> 00:07:52.144
Pastor Mark could see the glory on me.

00:07:52.144 --> 00:07:56.400
It’s just amazing.

00:07:56.400 --> 00:08:00.079
That’s how you know I live by faith.

00:08:00.426 --> 00:08:07.840
I expect angelic visitations and manifestations of the glory in my house.

00:08:07.840 --> 00:08:13.120
I expect God to do the impossible and I receive it.

00:08:13.554 --> 00:08:14.925
Let me tell you another one.

00:08:20.079 --> 00:08:20.319
There have been times when I’ve gone through a shady part of town and felt nervous.

00:08:20.991 --> 00:08:29.634
One time, I went to the gas station late at night—or it seemed late because it was winter and the sun goes down so early.

00:08:34.520 --> 00:08:36.752
I was nervous to get out of the car because of where I was and thought, 'Okay, here we go.

00:08:36.752 --> 00:08:43.999
' I went out there, and all of a sudden—because God loves you all and is compassionate—He opened my eyes for my comfort.

00:08:56.080 --> 00:08:58.853
He said, 'Look over, son.

00:08:58.853 --> 00:09:11.920
' I looked to my left, and there was a massive angel standing there watching over me as I was pumping gas.

00:09:13.100 --> 00:09:14.913
The angel was at attention.

00:09:14.913 --> 00:09:16.813
He had muscles upon muscles.

00:09:18.080 --> 00:09:27.400
He made Arnold Schwarzenegger look like a little weenie, like a little wimpy baby guy, or even some big bodybuilder, Mr.

00:09:27.400 --> 00:09:28.173
Universe.

00:09:28.173 --> 00:09:48.036
Olympics, like some guy that's ripped and has been eating nothing but protein, but this angel had muscle upon muscle and he was standing there decked out with this garb on, it looked like some kind of armor, and he was looking out at attention, watching over me.

00:09:48.036 --> 00:09:51.455
And when I saw that, it took me back.

00:09:53.890 --> 00:09:54.540
It took my breath and I went, "Whoa.

00:09:54.540 --> 00:09:58.183
" Because it's one of those things that shows God cares.

00:09:58.183 --> 00:09:58.651
God cares.

00:09:59.120 --> 00:10:05.230
And it blessed me so as he was watching out for me.

00:10:05.230 --> 00:10:14.971
It just shows that we have angels that keep charge over us and they bear us up in their hands lest we dash our foot against a stone.

00:10:14.971 --> 00:10:18.720
He promised us in Psalm 91 that he would do this.

00:10:18.720 --> 00:10:21.100
He promised us that he would take care of us.

00:10:21.100 --> 00:10:22.620
Do you believe it?

00:10:22.620 --> 00:10:24.114
Do you believe it?

00:10:24.114 --> 00:10:27.733
That Jesus is still the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:10:27.733 --> 00:10:32.200
And what he would do for the people in the Bible, he'll do for you.

00:10:32.200 --> 00:10:32.609
He'll protect you.

00:10:33.429 --> 00:10:36.640
Let me tell you another one.

00:10:36.640 --> 00:10:45.199
I was working at the church and I told you all about the healings whenever I'd led prayer and the angels bringing in hearts for people that needed hearts.

00:10:45.199 --> 00:10:56.960
For whatever reason, it was another heart testimony and I was just vacuuming the floor and I'm seeing over in this realm of the spirits when this happens.

00:10:58.790 --> 00:11:16.053
But this time the angel touched me and I literally thought I was going to come up out of my skin whenever he did it because I felt it on my shoulder and I was the only one in the room vacuuming the church and I went, "Whoa.

00:11:16.053 --> 00:11:24.870
" You get a little startled because the angel touched me like that and I turned around and I'm just seeing in the realm of spirit.

00:11:24.870 --> 00:11:36.640
It's not a physical manifestation, nothing like that; I'm looking in the realm of the spirit, but he touched me in the natural and he said, "I've come to give Jim a heart.

00:11:36.640 --> 00:11:40.560
" He goes, "You need to go and tell Jim that I've brought him a heart.

00:11:40.560 --> 00:11:41.080
" He's believing.

00:11:41.080 --> 00:11:42.773
He's been praying for a heart.

00:11:43.067 --> 00:11:45.849
They're believing for a miracle because Jim had a bad heart.

00:11:45.849 --> 00:11:48.468
And he was one of the other janitors on staff.

00:11:48.468 --> 00:11:51.510
And his blood pressure would drop bad, really bad.

00:11:51.973 --> 00:11:54.896
And he would have to go to the ER all the time.

00:11:54.896 --> 00:11:59.920
And it was very serious, some of the stuff that was happening with his heart.

00:11:59.920 --> 00:12:05.049
So the angel brought this heart and I could see in the spirit realm like I'm seeing my son right now.

00:12:05.049 --> 00:12:14.364
I mean it was that clear and the angel had a heart in his hand just like this—and, you know what, I take that back—it was in both hands.

00:12:14.364 --> 00:12:15.519
He had it in there.

00:12:15.519 --> 00:12:22.116
He brought it to me and he said, "Go and tell Jim that I brought the heart for him.

00:12:22.116 --> 00:12:25.227
" So I said, "Wow, okay, what an honor.

00:12:25.227 --> 00:12:39.706
" So I walk down the hall and I get all the way down the hall and Jim was in room number two because the rooms weren't labeled at this church, and he was in room two or three and I was cleaning on the back side of room 24.

00:12:39.706 --> 00:12:43.760
Not that that matters but I'm just telling you for the sake of the story.

00:12:43.760 --> 00:12:53.800
So I walked down the hall and I went in there and the angel went in there and I told Jim, "Jim, there's an angel of the Lord here and he has brought you a heart.

00:12:54.460 --> 00:12:55.840
Do you want to receive it?

00:12:55.840 --> 00:12:58.417
I'm going to pray for you and you're going to receive this heart.

00:12:58.417 --> 00:13:02.407
" He said, "Man, you ain't seeing nothing, dude.

00:13:02.407 --> 00:13:02.912
Whatever.

00:13:02.912 --> 00:13:04.200
Like, you're crazy.

00:13:04.200 --> 00:13:05.600
Get out of here, man.

00:13:06.420 --> 00:13:09.291
" He was totally pooh-poohing me.

00:13:09.291 --> 00:13:10.335
Like, "You're a weirdo.

00:13:10.335 --> 00:13:11.359
Get out of here.

00:13:11.359 --> 00:13:13.291
" And I was like, "No, really.

00:13:13.291 --> 00:13:16.010
I really see an angelic being.

00:13:16.010 --> 00:13:17.703
He wants to bring you a heart.

00:13:17.703 --> 00:13:18.480
He's brought you a heart.

00:13:18.480 --> 00:13:19.479
Do you want the heart?

00:13:19.479 --> 00:13:20.857
" He goes, "Dude, get out of here.

00:13:20.857 --> 00:13:21.440
Stop bothering me.

00:13:21.440 --> 00:13:21.867
That's weird.

00:13:25.040 --> 00:13:27.940
" I just looked at him and I went, "Okay, fine.

00:13:28.620 --> 00:13:31.828
" I was offended a little bit, like, "Whatever, dude.

00:13:33.040 --> 00:13:36.026
" I'm telling you, there's an angel here that wants to give you a heart.

00:13:36.026 --> 00:13:37.307
Do you want the heart or not?

00:13:37.307 --> 00:13:40.280
And I told the angel, I said, "He doesn't want the heart.

00:13:40.280 --> 00:13:41.640
You hear what he just said?

00:13:41.640 --> 00:13:43.911
" And I said, "I'm out of here.

00:13:43.911 --> 00:13:44.622
" And I walked away.

00:13:44.622 --> 00:13:46.537
And there's the angelic visitation.

00:13:46.537 --> 00:13:50.160
So, I go back and I get the vacuum cleaner again.

00:13:50.160 --> 00:13:52.354
And I'm just vacuuming the floors.

00:13:52.354 --> 00:13:55.988
And the angel of the Lord taps me on the shoulder again.

00:13:55.988 --> 00:14:02.005
He said, "Go one more time and ask Jim if he wants this heart.

00:14:02.005 --> 00:14:04.000
" I said, "You heard what he said.

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:05.260
He said he doesn't believe me.

00:14:05.260 --> 00:14:06.320
" And he made fun of me.

00:14:06.320 --> 00:14:07.839
I don't know what to do.

00:14:07.839 --> 00:14:10.339
He said, "Just go ask him one more time.

00:14:10.339 --> 00:14:11.719
" I said, "Okay.

00:14:11.719 --> 00:14:19.760
" So, I went down there and I said, "Jim, I'm coming because the angel asked me to ask you one more time.

00:14:19.760 --> 00:14:22.659
Do you want this heart?

00:14:22.659 --> 00:14:26.593
" He said, "You really do see something, don't you?

00:14:26.593 --> 00:14:27.279
You do?

00:14:27.279 --> 00:14:28.879
Like, Brandon, you really do?

00:14:28.879 --> 00:14:29.199
Like, really?

00:14:29.959 --> 00:14:33.382
" And I said, "Yeah, I'm telling you.

00:14:35.199 --> 00:14:35.529
" He was standing right there.

00:14:37.509 --> 00:14:39.973
I told him I could describe what he looked like.

00:14:39.973 --> 00:14:41.782
He goes, "Well, yeah.

00:14:43.018 --> 00:14:43.265
I need healing.

00:14:46.309 --> 00:14:54.955
" And I went over and I said, "In the name of Jesus, I command you to be healed of this heart condition.

00:14:54.955 --> 00:15:07.180
" And I watched that angel, I kid you not, drop that heart inside of Jim's chest.

00:15:07.180 --> 00:15:12.503
And I just said, "I believe you received it, brother.

00:15:12.503 --> 00:15:14.800
" The angel disappeared and was gone instantaneously.

00:15:14.800 --> 00:15:17.760
Within, I don't know, 24—whatever, he started getting better.

00:15:23.268 --> 00:15:27.000
His heart started getting better.

00:15:27.000 --> 00:15:32.069
Now, like I said, I don't know where Jim's at now.

00:15:34.868 --> 00:15:42.069
I haven't kept in contact with these people, but I'm telling you at that moment, I believe Jim got a new heart and his flesh started getting better.

00:15:42.069 --> 00:15:50.447
Now, Jim got caught up in drugs and alcohol and things like that and he backslid really, really hard.

00:15:50.447 --> 00:16:09.420
But I don't know, like I said, I don't know where these people are, but I'm telling you at that moment, I believe with all my heart Jesus Christ gave Jim a heart and the angel brought it.

00:16:09.420 --> 00:16:13.180
So, I wanted to encourage you all about that one.

00:16:19.573 --> 00:16:19.831
But, like I said, I have so many of these visitations and manifestations and demonstrations of the glory.

00:16:19.831 --> 00:16:21.795
I've told you all about my truck.

00:16:27.040 --> 00:16:32.656
My truck's supernaturally getting pushed down the highway for two and a half miles from where I live all the way to a gas station off of one of the roads.

00:16:32.656 --> 00:16:39.635
I won't tell you because it doesn't matter what street it was, but we were pushed by an angel.

00:16:40.737 --> 00:16:45.306
And if you go back and look at that, we ran out of gas.

00:16:46.372 --> 00:16:51.382
The gas gauge was out on my truck.

00:16:54.568 --> 00:16:58.870
I forgot that I had not put gas in there where we drove to work—it was a long drive.

00:16:58.870 --> 00:17:09.256
My wife was pregnant with my daughter at the time and my other two were in the back and it was hot, probably about 97 degrees outside or more.

00:17:09.256 --> 00:17:12.280
A hot summer day.

00:17:12.280 --> 00:17:14.680
It was in the middle of July.

00:17:16.780 --> 00:17:23.399
And my truck turns off in the middle of the highway and I go over to the side.

00:17:35.380 --> 00:17:35.680
I put my hazard lights on and I told my wife, "Baby, I'm going to have to walk to the gas station.

00:17:36.880 --> 00:17:37.627
" And she's big and pregnant.

00:17:38.373 --> 00:17:41.200
And I'm thinking, "This is going to be really, really bad.

00:17:41.200 --> 00:17:45.220
" And I just start praying in the spirit.

00:17:46.686 --> 00:17:47.989
We're all just praying in the spirit.

00:17:47.989 --> 00:17:54.023
And lo and behold, we have this massive boom.

00:17:54.023 --> 00:18:11.897
And I think somebody has hit us, rear-ending us from behind, and our whole truck jerked and all of a sudden we started going faster and faster down the highway.

00:18:11.897 --> 00:18:20.320
I put my blinker on and I'm riding in the shoulder and I merge onto the highway with the engine off.

00:18:20.320 --> 00:18:24.756
Whether you want to believe this or not, it's the truth.

00:18:24.756 --> 00:18:26.960
We're going down the highway.

00:18:26.960 --> 00:18:35.147
I'm going 70 mph with the engine off, passing people in the left-hand lane as I'm going down the highway with the truck off.

00:18:35.147 --> 00:18:38.891
That angel's pushing us all the way down through the—we exit off.

00:18:40.839 --> 00:18:41.119
We stop at the stoplight.

00:18:44.960 --> 00:18:45.360
The angel pushes us through the stoplight.

00:18:45.360 --> 00:18:50.630
Go all the way down to another stop sign and turn right.

00:18:50.630 --> 00:19:01.404
It pushes us through it, and then, yank, we get to the gas station, and it yanks the tailgate of our truck and stops us right in front of the pump.

00:19:16.480 --> 00:19:16.800
We all started screaming and praising the Lord because it was so supernatural what the Lord had just done right then.

00:19:29.733 --> 00:19:30.107
The other people at the other pumps were looking at us like, "What is going on with these people?

00:19:30.107 --> 00:19:48.840
" because we were just screaming; it was just one of those moments where you're just shaking because what's happening in the natural is coming from the supernatural and God is coming through for you again.

00:19:53.440 --> 00:19:53.760
We got pushed all the way to the gas station.

00:19:53.760 --> 00:19:59.869
I've told this story before, but it's worth telling again because it's all God and He's worthy to be praised.

00:19:59.869 --> 00:20:05.312
He's been faithful to me, and I've got to give Him the praise for it again.

00:20:05.312 --> 00:20:11.822
Then I told you all about the hospital where my wife had no pain.

00:20:14.548 --> 00:20:15.876
The angel came in and laid hands on my wife during our first pregnancy.

00:20:15.876 --> 00:20:22.491
We were believing for a supernatural childbirth and no pain through childbirth.

00:20:33.370 --> 00:20:33.720
My wife was in labor with our daughter, Megan, at the time.

00:20:33.720 --> 00:20:45.200
The angel came in and laid his hands on her stomach, and up until my wife was almost completely through delivery, she felt nothing.

00:20:45.200 --> 00:20:51.337
She felt contractions—her body was contracting—but she had no pain at all.

00:20:51.337 --> 00:21:01.900
Even the doctor and the people coming in—we had family trying to visit, and people go, "Why would you have people come up?

00:21:01.900 --> 00:21:03.039
" We learned our lesson.

00:21:03.039 --> 00:21:06.720
Family would try to come up and say, "That's impossible.

00:21:06.720 --> 00:21:08.663
They say you can't do that.

00:21:10.560 --> 00:21:13.954
" All of a sudden, that angel took his hand.

00:21:13.954 --> 00:21:18.867
There was so much doubt and unbelief in the room.

00:21:18.867 --> 00:21:22.320
I've told you that.

00:21:24.960 --> 00:21:28.320
You get shaken by people speaking negatively around you about what God's doing.

00:21:28.320 --> 00:21:30.880
Even the doctors were saying that's impossible.

00:21:45.978 --> 00:21:46.169
The nurses, they all look at you like you're wild.

00:21:46.169 --> 00:21:54.470
They don't understand how my wife was not having any pain during childbirth, but God was doing something supernatural.

00:21:54.470 --> 00:21:58.880
This was very vital—it's very important that you learn from this.

00:21:58.880 --> 00:22:06.860
Do not let negativity into your hospital room when you are believing for a miracle because it's a robber of your faith.

00:22:10.862 --> 00:22:16.506
You hear doubt and unbelief, and just like faith cometh by hearing and hearing by the Word of God, doubt comes by hearing fear.

00:22:16.506 --> 00:22:24.906
When Jesus was raising the little girl up from the dead, He made all the other people leave the room that didn't have faith.

00:22:24.906 --> 00:22:29.380
He got them out of the house.

00:22:29.380 --> 00:22:35.349
There's a reason for that: because it robs faith.

